{
  "stem": "7094.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was-- it lasted three days, the action.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they were going through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They didn't find anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were going through.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had this sort of hay, although it was town, but in the little hiding space.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I could hear a German coming and probing with a-- with his bayonet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I walked out, thinking that my sister would remain there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when I came to the synagogue, to the meeting place, I was on my own.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I said, oh, fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They are still there, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They are hiding.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But gradually, gradually, as it was three days, I found my grandmother, my aunt, my sister.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But my mother and my younger sister were not there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Over this-- And then eventually they asked us to walk to the station.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I think I mentioned to you the station was about 1 and 1/2 or 2 kilometers from town, and we had to walk.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And this was already-- I could see it coming, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "First of all, the shooting was going on all along, anybody who couldn't keep space-- pace.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then in front of us, the first day they shot the Judenrat, you know, the main dealer, wheeler, who used to be the god in a way, you know, who could-- who-- who was the go-between.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He was shot straightaway, so we straightaway realize, you know, how serious-- whether this is the end.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And as we were walking, people were shot on the way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we came to the train, and then I met-- my younger sister was taken in the last minute where we were loaded into the trains.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And she came to me and said, don't be angry with me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I won't cry, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
